'''Tim Stowers''' was the head coach of the [[Georgia Southern Eagles football|Georgia Southern Eagles]] and [[Rhode Island Rams football|Rhode Island Rams]] football teams. He compiled an 84<U+2013>80<U+2013>0 overall record, including the 1990 NCAA Division I-AA National Championship and the 1993 [[Southern Conference]] Championship.

